OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMPs can claim Christmas    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fparties on expenses - Ipsa 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MPs will be able to claim the cost of  
OL,6, their office Christmas party on        
OL,7, parliamentary expenses under new rules.
OL,9,FThe Independent Parliamentary Standards
OL,10,FAuthority (Ipsa) announced MPs can this
OL,11,Fyear claim back money spent on food,   
OL,12,Fdecorations and non-alcoholic drinks   
OL,13,Ffor an "office festive event".         
OL,15,FMPs can also claim for a party in their
OL,16,Fconstituency if it is "within a        
OL,17,Fparliamentary context".                
OL,19,FThe move has been criticised by MPs    
OL,20,Ffrom all sides of Parliament.          
